name: Global X Enhanced S&P/TSX 60 Covered Call ETF
longDescription: The ETF seeks to provide, to the extent reasonably possible and net of expenses exposure to the performance of the large-cap market segment of the Canadian equity market; and high monthly distributions of dividend and call option income. To generate income, the ETF will be exposed to a dynamic covered call option writing program. The ETF will also employ leverage through cash borrowing and will generally endeavour to maintain a leverage ratio of approximately 125%. To generate income, the ETF will be exposed to a dynamic covered call option writing program.
